            <h5>Customizer Rating: <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star-half-stroke"></i><i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i></i></h5>
